OL,6,F Jonathan Brown talks to Dr Kelly
OL,7,FFearnley about the severe impact of
OL,8,Flong CovidJA doctor who is leading a
OL,9,Fbid to sue the NHS for failing to
OL,10,Fprovide frontline staff with adequate
OL,11,Fprotective equipment during the
OL,12,Fpandemic says workers were
OL,13,F"deliberately and repeatedly" exposed
OL,14,Fto Covid.
