OL,6,FDr Fearnley volunteered to treat Covid
OL,7,Fpatients after graduating from Leeds
OL,8,FMedical School in spring 2020.JShe
OL,9,Fsaid in the early months of the
OL,10,Fpandemic she was wearing high grade
OL,11,FPPE and did not catch Covid.JBut when
OL,12,Fshe was deployed to a Covid ward at
OL,13,FBradford Royal Infirmary during a
OL,14,Fsurge in infections in November 2020,
OL,15,Fshe was only given a surgical mask.
OL,17,FShe told ITV News: "I spent about ten
OL,18,Fhours for five consecutive days on a
OL,19,FCovid ward surrounded by Covid
OL,20,Fpatients all coughing and breathing
OL,21,Fand speaking into the air.
