OL,6,F"So essentially (I was) in a Covid
OL,7,Fsuit, unprotected, or inadequately
OL,8,Fprotected. Then I fell unwell after
OL,9,Fthat. I tested positive two days after
OL,10,Fthat."JDr Fearnley later suffered
OL,11,Fcomplications and continues to feel
OL,12,Fthe effects of the virus.
