OL,6,FShe said: "I've experienced violent
OL,7,Fshaking. I used to shake for 14 hours
OL,8,Fat a time. It's damaged my hearing. I
OL,9,Fexperienced brain inflammation. I
OL,10,Fspent several weeks hallucinating. I
OL,11,Fspent the first year (after infection)
OL,12,Fbed-bound. The second year mostly bed-
OL,13,Fbound."JShe says the illness has
OL,14,F"impacted every aspect" of her life
OL,15,Fand left her unable to pursue her
OL,16,Fambition of working in emergency
OL,17,Fmedicine.
