OL,6,FShe added that while she had seen some
OL,7,F"slow improvement", a survey found one
OL,8,Fin five doctors who caught Covid could
OL,9,Fnot return to work.JShe said: "They
OL,10,Fstill find it difficult to feed
OL,11,Fthemselves, to get dressed, to take
OL,12,Fcare of their children. Doctors have
OL,13,Fnot only lost their health and
OL,14,Findependence. Many are now facing
OL,15,Ffinancial destitution."JDr Fearnley
OL,16,Fsaid some doctors had been forced to
OL,17,Fsell their homes because of the
OL,18,Ffinancial impact.JShe blamed the
OL,19,FGovernment for downgrading healthcare
OL,20,Fworkers' PPE during the pandemic,
OL,21,Fsaying the decision "was not based on
OL,22,Fscience".
